      },
      "writtenOn": "2019-09-10T19:55:53Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "So, to clarify, any function in crash_report_database_generic that wishes to open a directory without having a message logged should first call IsDirectory() and then call DirectoryReader::Open()?",
